"""test_error_ex3"""
result = subprocess.run(['python3', './GC_analysis/GC_analysis.py', '-i',
    './tests/ex3.fasta', '-o', './tests/ex3.fasta.wig', '-w', '5', '-s',
    '5'], stderr=subprocess.PIPE, stdout=subprocess.PIPE)
assert result.stderr.split(b'\n')[-2] == b'TypeError'
assert result.returncode == 1
assert result.stdout[-28:] == b' contains no sequence data.\n'
